mixin present-block
    #home.row.cs-presentation
        .col-md-12
            .cs-title-line
            h2.cs-title Presentation

            iframe(
                width='854'
                height='480'
                src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/FSX3r4RVBxg?showinfo=0&modestbranding=1'
                frameborder='0'
                gesture='media'
                allow='encrypted-media'
                allowfullscreen
            ).center-block.cs-video
            
            +social-icons.cs-social-bright

    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/1.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Have you ever felt like you had a great idea? Some cool idea for anything: movie, app, video game, startup?
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/2.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p But how to finance your startup project? Who's going to invest in your idea?
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/3.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p You probably heard of crowdfunding. platforms like Kickstarter, Indigogo, etc.
    hr        
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/4.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p What are the benefits of crowdfunding? Crowdfunding helps raise money by selling a product directly to your customers before product creation.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/5.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p This allows validation of an idea by your customers.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/6.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p This also creates a relationship with your future customers instantly, alowing a quick communication channel and feedback.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/7.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Campaigners have nothing more than a promise to give to their backers.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/8.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Ownership of a future product can not be transferred to others.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/9.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Setting up a crowdfunding campaign to accept crypto currency is complicated.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/10.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Say hello to CryptoStarter.io. 
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/11.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p With CryptoStarter campaigners can create their own project tokens, which can be redeemed for a product, can be used as a digital share of a future company, or be traded.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/12.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Cryptostarter creates an instant marketplace for project tokens. Since the amount of project tokens is set to be limited, the price changes. Buy or Sell project tokens right beforeproduct release.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            img(src='img/present/13.png').cs-present-img.cs-present-img-double.center-block
            p Anyone holding a cryptostarter token IDEA-coin, receives 3.5% Rewards from every crowdfunding campgain on the platform.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/14.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Lets see how it works. Meet Alice. Alice wants to launch a crowdfunding campaign - AliceSmartGadget. She submits new project.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/15.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Sets the number of Tokens to 1000. 1 product is 1 token.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/16.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Sets planned delivery to 6 month. Launched! That's it!
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/17.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Meet Bob! Bob finds a cool project from Alice listed in project Library.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/18.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Bob buys 5 Alice's Tokens with FIAT or Cryptocurrency.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/19.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p And keeps them in CS-Wallet.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-6
            img(src='img/present/20.png').cs-present-img.cs-present-img-double.center-block
            p After 3 month Bob decides to sell 4 tokens to investor - Chester, who just discovered the project.
        .col-md-6
            img(src='img/present/21.png').cs-present-img.cs-present-img-double.center-block
            p Chester buys 4 tokens from Bob, using CS.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/22.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p After 6 month Alice releases the product.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/23.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Meanwhile more people got interested. Chester sells 3 tokens for a higher price.
        .col-md-4
            img(src='img/present/24.png').cs-present-img.center-block
            p Bob and Chester redeem their tokens to get the product.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            img(src='img/present/25.png').cs-present-img.cs-present-img-double.center-block
            p Cryptostarter has IDEA token and gives reward distribution for all holders. 3.5% of each project gets distributed proportionally to all IDEA token holders.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-6
            img(src='img/present/26.png').cs-present-img.cs-present-img-double.center-block
            p Letâ€™s recap how Cryptostarter works in 4 simple steps. Step 1 Submit the project. Step 2. Project tokens get generated and listed on exchange.
        .col-md-6
            img(src='img/present/27.png').cs-present-img.cs-present-img-double.center-block
            p Step 3. Tokens get bought and sold before product release. Step 4. Tokens get redeemed with a product upon release.
    hr
    .row.cs-comics-row
        .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            img(src='img/present/28.svg').cs-present-img.cs-present-img-double.center-block
            p CryptoStarter.io
    hr        